## GitHub Actions CI: File Creation & Triggers
Create `.github/workflows/ci.yml`. Define triggers, e.g., `on: push/pull_request: branches: [main]`.

## GitHub Actions CI: Commit & Push Workflow File
`git add .github/workflows/ci.yml`, `git commit ...`, `git push ...`.

## GitHub Actions CI: Trigger Workflow via PR
`gh pr create --base main --fill`.

## GitHub Actions CI: Monitoring Runs (Recommended)
Avoid `gh run watch [| cat]` (needs ID non-interactively).
1. Get ID: `gh run list --limit 1 --json databaseId -q '.[0].databaseId' | cat`
2. Watch ID: `gh run watch <RUN_ID> --exit-status | cat`

## GitHub Actions CI: Troubleshooting Lockfile Mismatch (`ERR_PNPM_OUTDATED_LOCKFILE`)
Run `pnpm install`, then `git add pnpm-lock.yaml`, `git commit -m "fix: update pnpm lockfile"`, `git push`.

## GitHub Actions CI: Viewing Logs
`gh run view <RUN_ID> --log | cat`.